5
00:00:38,770 --> 00:00:40,840
这就是我的一天
Here's my day,so far.

6
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:44,920
蹲过监狱 失去我爱的女孩 还被臭打了一顿
Went to jail,lost the girl of my dreams and got my butt kicked.

7
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,150
很好
Pretty good.

8
00:00:46,690 --> 00:00:49,770
情况可能会更糟糕
Still,things could be a lot worse.

9
00:00:50,670 --> 00:00:54,660
对了 我马上要摔死了
Oh,that's right,I'm falling to my death.

10
00:00:55,350 --> 00:00:56,810
不是吧
Guess they can't.

11
00:00:57,570 --> 00:00:59,430
你会问 这是怎么回事?
How did it all come to this,you ask?

12
00:01:00,670 --> 00:01:02,440
我的结局在开始就被注定
My end starts at the beginning.

13
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,660
从出生开始
The very beginning.

14
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:10,070
没错 那就是我
Yes,that's me.

15
00:01:10,810 --> 00:01:13,700
我有过短暂但正常的"童"年
I had a fairly standard childhood.

16
00:01:14,590 --> 00:01:17,650
我出身在一个通常所说的 破碎的家庭
I came from what you might call,a broken home.

17
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:21,060
破碎是字面上的
Literally,broken.

18
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:24,280
出生八天后就再也没见过父母
I was eight days old and still living with my parents.

19
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,330
有够悲催的吧?
How sad is that?

20
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:28,820
命运齿轮开始转动
Clearly it was time to move on.

21
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:32,070
这是Minion 它会照顾你
Here is your,Minion,he will take care of you.

22
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:33,830
拿好你的奶嘴
And here is your binkie.

23
00:01:33,980 --> 00:01:37,050
你命中注定会...
You are destined for ...

24
00:01:37,050 --> 00:01:38,860
我没听清最后半句
I didn't quite hear that last part.

25
00:01:38,860 --> 00:01:40,500
貌似很重要
But it sounded important.

26
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:43,230
命中注定 干什么?
Destined for,what?

27
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:48,020
我出发去寻找命运
I set out to find my destiny.

28
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:53,690
看来另一个来自蓝宝象限的孩子也这么想
Turns out a kid from the Blaupunkt quadrant had the exact same idea.

29
00:02:00,740 --> 00:02:03,900
那天我遇见 "比别人都强" 先生
That was the day I met,Mr.Goody-two-shoes.

30
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:11,330
咱们的最佳对手竞争拉开了序幕
And our glorious rivalry,was born!

31
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:18,440
啊 这就是我的命运?
Could this be what I was destined for?

32
00:02:18,830 --> 00:02:21,320
如梦如幻的奢华生活?
A dream life filled with luxury?

33
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,620
显然不是
Apparently not.

34
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:28,510
就连命运也挑喜欢的
Even fate picks its favorites.

35
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,480
没什么大不了
No big deal.

36
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:33,840
一个截然不同的未来等着我
A much different fate awaited me.

37
00:02:41,770 --> 00:02:43,100
是小宝宝哎
A baby.

38
00:02:43,370 --> 00:02:44,740
考虑太周到了
How thoughtful.

39
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:48,130
没错 我看见他就想起你
Oh yes,yes.I saw it and thought of you.

40
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:51,920
总算有个小地方是我家了
Luckily I found a lovely little place to call home.

41
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:53,350
我们可以养他吗?
Can we keep it?

42
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:57,410
那里教我什么是对...
A place that taught me the differences between right...

43
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,140
...什么是错
...and wrong.

44
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:02,100
而 "比别人都强" 先生
Mr.Goody-Two-Shoes on the other hand,

45
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:04,670
衣来伸手 饭来张口
had life handed to him on a silver platter.

46
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,100
咱家的宝宝会飞哎
Our baby can fly.

47
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:09,630
没错 你的都是最好的 亲爱的
Yes,yes.Nothing but the best for you,Darling.

48
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:14,030
他有飞行力 刀枪不入 发型也不错
The power of flight,invulnerability,and great hair.

49
00:03:14,990 --> 00:03:17,940
但有项我比他强的多
But I had something far,far greater,

50
00:03:17,940 --> 00:03:19,570
那就是聪明才智
My amazing intellect.

51
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:22,750
我能把犯罪工具造得出神入化
A knack for building objects of mayhem.

52
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:32,110
几年后 因为表现良好
After a few years,and with some time off for good behavior.

53
00:03:32,730 --> 00:03:36,430
我被允许上学来改造自己
I was given an opportunity to better myself through learning.

54
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:40,130
那个奇怪的地方叫学 "笑"
At a strange place called shh-ool.

55
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:44,540
在那里我又遇到了 "比别人都强" 先生
It was there that I once again ran into Mr.Goody-Two-Shoes.

56
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:48,640
显然他已经有N个没脑子的仰慕者了
He had already amassed a gigantic army of soft-headed groupies.

57
00:03:55,130 --> 00:04:00,080
他靠生动表演和香喷喷的米花 讨大家喜欢
He bought their affections with showmanship,and extravagant gifts of deliciousness.

58
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:07,040
哼 看我的 "爆玉米花" 让这群呆子大吃一惊
So I too would make this 'popped-corn' and win over those mindless dregs.

59
00:04:07,050 --> 00:04:08,060
熄灯了!
Lights out!

60
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:28,530
那次我学到了艰难的一课
That's when I learned a very hard lesson.

61
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:31,360
英雄生来满载赞扬和奉承
Good receives all the praise and adulation.

62
00:04:31,370 --> 00:04:34,390
坏蛋就活该面壁思过
While evil is sent to quiet time in the corner.

63
00:04:35,660 --> 00:04:38,060
于是我注定无法跟别人相处
So a fitting end wasn't really an option.

64
00:04:39,370 --> 00:04:42,700
当他们在学可爱小蜘蛛时
While they were learning the itsy bitsy spider.

65
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:45,420
我学会怎么给活物脱水
I learned how to dehydrate animate objects.

66
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:47,380
和怎样任意再水化它们
and rehydrate them at will.

67
00:04:48,450 --> 00:04:53,460
有时感觉只有Minion和我在一起 与全世界为敌
Some days it felt like it was just me and Minion,against the world.

68
00:04:54,370 --> 00:04:56,610
不管怎么努力
No matter how hard I tried.

69
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:58,800
我永远都不合群
I was always the odd man out.

70
00:04:58,810 --> 00:05:00,680
是剩下的那个
The last one picked.

71
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:03,210
永远一团糟 是害群之马
The screw-up,the black sheep.

72
00:05:04,210 --> 00:05:06,460
是不良少年
The bad boy.

73
00:05:14,310 --> 00:05:15,310
哦!
Oh!

74
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:19,490
这就是我的命运?
Was this my destiny?

75
00:05:19,850 --> 00:05:22,540
等等!也许没错
Wait!Maybe it was.

76
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:26,350
当坏蛋不就是我最擅长的吗
Being bad is the one thing I'm good at.

77
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,250
我恍然大悟
Then it hit me.

78
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,860
如果我是个坏孩子
If I was the bad boy.

79
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:34,890
我就要坏到彻底
Then I was going to be the baddest boy of them all.

80
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:38,780
我注定会成为超级大坏蛋
I was destined to be a super villain.

81
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:42,130
我们注定是对手
And we were destined to be rivals.

82
00:05:43,150 --> 00:05:45,200
命运就这样决定了
The die had been cast.

83
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:49,470
我的永恒史诗 毕生事业就此拉开序幕
And so began an enduring epic,life long career.

84
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,710
我爱这项事业
And I loved it.

85
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:56,190
我们的战斗很快变得越来越复杂
Our battles quickly got more elaborate.

86
00:05:56,320 --> 00:06:00,940
他赢几次 我也不甘示弱
He would win some,I would almost win others.

87
00:06:01,090 --> 00:06:03,720
他有个大名 都市侠
He took the name,Metro Man.

88
00:06:03,730 --> 00:06:05,920
大都会守卫者
Defender of Montrosity.

89
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:08,640
我的名字呢 就谦卑多了
I decided to pick something a little more humble.

90
00:06:08,650 --> 00:06:09,710
超级大坏蛋
Megamind.

91
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:14,610
史上最帅犯罪天才 精通各种恶行
Incredibly handsome criminal genius,and master of all villainy.

92
00:06:25,770 --> 00:06:28,370
下班了再看 开门
Read on your own time.Open up.

93
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,000
嗨
Hey!

94
00:06:36,010 --> 00:06:37,050
嘘
BOO!!

95
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,250
早上好 典狱长
Oh,good morning,Warden.

96
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:44,890
好消息哦 我改过自新了
Great news,I'm a changed man.

97
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:48,940
作为可靠市民 我可以重返社会了
And I'm ready to re-enter society as a solid citizen.

98
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:51,690
你是个罪犯 而且永远是个罪犯
You're a villain,and you'll always be a villain.

99
00:06:51,690 --> 00:06:53,060
你根本没有改过
You'll never change.

100
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:54,670
也就别想着离开
And you'll never leave.

101
00:06:54,670 --> 00:06:57,620
- 你真搞笑 - 有人给你邮了份礼物
-You're fun. - You got a present in the mail.

102
00:06:57,620 --> 00:06:59,280
是小狗吗?
Is it a puppy?

103
00:06:59,290 --> 00:07:04,020
都市侠给你的 "珍惜你85次无期徒刑的每分每秒吧"
From Metro Man.To count every second of your 85 life sentences.

104
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:07,200
真搞笑 没想到都市侠也会落井下石
That's funny,never thought Metro Man was the gloating type.

105
00:07:07,450 --> 00:07:09,080
但他品位确实不错
Oh but he does have nice taste.

106
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,480
我帮你保管吧
I think I'll keep it.

107
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,500
能不能别再拖时间了?
Any chance you could give me the time?

108
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:15,800
今天都市侠博物馆开张 我可不想迟到
I don't want to be late for the opening of the Metro Man museum.

109
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:19,420
哦不 看来你要错过了
Oh no,looks like you're gonna miss it.

110
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:21,510
错过好几千年哪
By several thousand years.

111
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:25,870
噢 是吗?
Oh,am I?

112
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:32,130
大都会市民们 都市侠日快乐
Happy Metro Man day,Metro City.

113
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:40,130
今日天朗气清 市中心整洁有序 我们即将迎来一位绅士的光临
It's a beautiful day in beautiful downtown where we're here to honor a beautiful man.

114
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:41,900
都市侠
Metro Man.

115
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:46,280
他的心胸似海洋 但更宽广
His heart is an ocean that's inside a bigger ocean.

116
00:07:46,610 --> 00:07:49,580
这些年 他的超级视力一直守卫着我们
For years he's been watching us with his super-vision.

117
00:07:49,860 --> 00:07:54,530
超能力一直解救我们 博爱之心也关照我们
Saving us with his super strength,and caring for us with his super heart.

118
00:07:54,530 --> 00:07:57,170
现在是我们回报他的时候了
Now it's our turn to give something back.

119
00:07:57,650 --> 00:08:02,150
这里是Roxanne Ritchi为您 在都市侠博物馆落成典礼发回现场报道
This is Roxanne Ritchi reporting live,from the dedication of the Metro Man Museum.

120
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:05,040
刚才他们让你在广播里念的那一段
Wow,okay,the stuff they make you read on the air.

121
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,430
真难以置信 都疯了吧
That's unfreaking believable,it's crazy.

122
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:09,250
那是我自己写的 Hal
I wrote that piece myself,Hal.

123
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:11,390
其实我想说的是
What I was trying to say was,

124
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:17,110
在现代社会的新闻里还能出现艺术的闪光 真是难得啊
I can't believe that in our modern society they let like actual art get onto the news.

125
00:08:17,110 --> 00:08:20,380
- 补得漂亮 Hal - 我们去喝杯咖啡什么的吧
-Nice save,Hal. - What are we,like lets just get a coffee or something.

126
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:23,470
今天可是都市侠的大日子
Come on,it's time to get in the Metro Man day spirit.

127
00:08:23,470 --> 00:08:27,100
如果我是都市侠 决不会让大坏蛋绑架你那么多次
Well,if I were Metro Man Megamind wouldn't be kidnapping you all the time.

128
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:28,470
这是最重要的事
That's the first thing.

129
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,930
你真贴心
That's sweet of you.

130
00:08:29,930 --> 00:08:33,100
我会像澳洲野狗看孩子一样看着你
And I'd be watching you,like a dingo watches a human baby.

131
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:35,680
- 呃 - 听起来有点怪
-Mmm. - Okay,that sounded,Okay that sounded a little weird.

132
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:36,880
确实有一点
A little bit,yeah.

133
00:08:36,890 --> 00:08:39,360
你脸色怪怪的 我说什么好呢
And you're making a weird face,and that's making me feel weird.

134
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:45,400
不是爱啦 我们又没谈恋爱 我不是说我爱你
Not love,we're not in love.I'm not saying I love you.

135
00:08:45,410 --> 00:08:48,010
好吧 我爱你 哎呀其实我也不是这个意思
Okay,I love you,whatever.I'm not saying like I'm in love with you.

136
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:51,820
我是说...Roxanne?Roxaroo?
I'm saying...Roxanne?Roxaroo?

137
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:08,110
好好上班
Get back to work.

138
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:10,290
政府花钱不是让你游手好闲的
The city doesn't pay you to loaf.

139
00:09:10,710 --> 00:09:12,060
- 不许动! - 你们要干什么 伙计们?
-Freeze! - Whoa,what are you doing,guys?

140
00:09:12,060 --> 00:09:14,160
是我!我是典狱长
It's ME!It's the Warden.

141
00:09:14,830 --> 00:09:16,160
喂 开门
Hey,open up.

142
00:09:23,820 --> 00:09:26,400
你们个蠢蛋 都被他玩了
Oh,you fools.He's tricked us.

143
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,950
你说得没错
You were right.

144
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,160
我一直都会是个大坏蛋
I'll always be a villain.

145
00:09:31,620 --> 00:09:34,790
<i>'坏到入骨' - George Thorogood<i>
<i>George Thorogood's 'Bad to the Bone'</i>

146
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:40,590
<i>坏到入骨 坏到入骨<i>
<i>Bad to the bone.Bad to the bone.</i>

147
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:45,490
<i>坏...坏...<i>
<i>B..B..B..Bad.B..B..B..Bad.</i>

148
00:09:45,490 --> 00:09:49,030
<i>坏到入骨<i>
<i>Bad to the bone.</i>

149
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:51,610
哎呀帅锅 要搭车吗?
Well hello good looking,need a lift?

150
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:54,050
当然要啦 大美鱼
Certainly do,you fantastic fish you.

151
00:09:54,050 --> 00:09:55,940
快上车吧
Get in the car,you.

152
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,720
哟吼 我自由了
Whoo,I'm free.

153
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:01,680
你的手表棒极了 Minion
Thanks for sending me the watch,Minion.

154
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:02,900
那还用说 老板
You got it,boss.

155
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:04,650
冲啊
Punch it.

156
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:08,480
来吧 把双手举高
All right,put your hands in the air.

157
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:16,090
女士们绅士们 欢迎都市侠
Ladies and gentlemen,your Metro Man.

158
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:19,370
- 你们在等谁? - 都市侠
-Who's your Man? - Metro man.

159
00:10:19,770 --> 00:10:22,560
你好 大都会!
Yeah,Metro City!

160
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:28,420
来吧 把手都给我 怎么样?
Give me some,come on give it now.Give it to me.What?

161
00:10:28,430 --> 00:10:30,320
来击掌吧...非常好!
Give it to me...all right!

162
00:10:32,410 --> 00:10:35,990
你 嗨 哈 哈 你
Yo,hey,ha,ha yo.

163
00:10:48,010 --> 00:10:49,420
你好 大都会
Hey,Metro city.

164
00:10:50,940 --> 00:10:52,290
你好
Hello,hey.

165
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:55,940
好了 大家都冷静一点吧
You know,I just want you to bring it down a bit.

166
00:10:56,190 --> 00:10:57,310
小伙子们 小点声
Boys,a little lower.

167
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,720
谢谢
Thank you fellows.

168
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:01,150
我们现在说点实际的
Let's get real for a moment.

169
00:11:01,490 --> 00:11:04,240
没错 就是那样
That's right,that's right ha,ha,that's right.

170
