Oh no.Somebody do something?

867
00:50:57,770 --> 00:51:00,250
对 对 我来救你了
Oh,right,right.Duh!I gotcha.

868
00:51:06,280 --> 00:51:09,670
真好玩 你差点死了 但我救了你
That was fun,you almost died.But I saved you.

869
00:51:09,670 --> 00:51:11,230
