-Aaaah,building! - AH!

870
00:51:15,610 --> 00:51:16,710
接住了!
Gotcha!

871
00:51:16,710 --> 00:51:19,330
不好意思 你刚说什么?
Whoo,I'm sorry.What were you saying?

872
00:51:19,330 --> 00:51:21,690
我听不见 被我救你的声音覆盖了
I couldn't hear you over the sound of me saving your life.

873
00:51:21,690 --> 00:51:23,310
放下我 马上!
Put me down,right now!

874
00:51:23,310 --> 00:51:25,850
好吧 好吧 抓紧了
Okay,all right,all right,hold on.

875
00:51:28,480 --> 00:51:29,810
你疯了吗?
Are you crazy?

876
00:51:29,810 --> 00:51:33,490
我想我是有点疯狂...为了你
I suppose I'm,a little crazy...about you.

877
00:51:33,490 --> 00:51:35,160
你是谁?说真的
Who are you?Really.

878
00:51:35,180 --> 00:51:40,170
好吧 准备大吃一惊吧 小姐
Oooh,oooh,right.Well prepare to have your mind blown,little lady.

879
00:51:41,340 --> 00:51:43,530
- 看! - Hal?
-Tada! - Hal?

880
00:51:43,530 --> 00:51:45,900
是啊 这不是很好吗?
Yeah,isn't this great?

881
00:51:45,900 --> 00:51:48,070
没有什么能把我们分开了
Now there's nothing keeping us apart.

882
00:51:48,070 --> 00:51:49,990
不 一点也不好
No,it's not great.

883
00:51:49,990 --> 00:51:54,360
我们的第一次飞行 太浪漫了 就像一对老夫老妻
Wow,our first fight.This is so us,we're like an old married couple.

884
00:51:54,360 --> 00:51:57,510
没有我们 我们永远不可能
There is no us,okay.There will never be an us.

885
00:51:57,510 --> 00:51:59,990
但是我有力量
But,I have powers.

886
00:51:59,990 --> 00:52:02,780
我有斗篷 我是好人
I have a cape,I'm the good guy.

887
00:52:02,780 --> 00:52:03,550
你是好人 Hal
You are a good guy,Hal.

888
00:52:03,550 --> 00:52:06,840
但你不明白为什么...
But you don't understand we need to find out why...

889
00:52:06,840 --> 00:52:08,830
