是Titan 不是Hal
It's Tighten.It's TIGHTEN,not Hal.

893
00:52:40,060 --> 00:52:42,070
- Bernard． - Roxanne．
-Bernard. - Roxanne.

894
00:52:42,080 --> 00:52:45,750
- 对不起我迟到了 - 你的头发很刺激
-Sorry I'm late. - Wow,your hair looks exciting.

895
00:52:45,750 --> 00:52:48,900
今晚不止是头发很刺激
Hmm,not the only exciting development of the night.

896
00:52:48,920 --> 00:52:51,360
