Megamind's created a new hero.

897
00:52:51,360 --> 00:52:52,700
我知道原因
And I know why.

898
00:52:53,750 --> 00:52:55,290
一切都说得通了
It all makes sense now.

899
00:52:55,300 --> 00:52:59,850
