Hal is the worst possible person you could pick.

902
00:53:05,750 --> 00:53:08,100
这很难理解
Wow,that's a lot to take in.

903
00:53:08,110 --> 00:53:09,940
让我大吃一惊
It,it boggles my mind.

904
00:53:09,940 --> 00:53:11,940
我也很惊讶
I am extremely boggled.

905
00:53:11,950 --> 00:53:15,300
谁踢谁的屁股一定会见分晓
You know,I'm sure we'll get to the bottom of who's kicking who's butt.

906
00:53:15,300 --> 00:53:16,310
但与此同时
But in the mean time.

907
00:53:17,220 --> 00:53:19,630
让我们先享受在一起的时光吧
Let's enjoy each other's company.

908
00:53:19,630 --> 00:53:22,870
抱歉 Bernard 你说得对
I'm sorry,Bernard.Of course,your right,

909
00:53:22,870 --> 00:53:25,810
我应该先喘口气
you know,I could use a breather.

910
00:53:25,820 --> 00:53:31,610
为了Bernard 为你是我疯狂世界中 唯一正常的人
To,Bernard.For being the only normal thing in my crazy upside down world.

911
00:53:31,620 --> 00:53:34,920
为了...正常
To...being normal.

912
00:53:45,220 --> 00:53:47,310
