-Roxanne. - Yes?

913
00:53:48,470 --> 00:53:50,510
如果我不是正常人
Say I wasn't so normal.

914
00:53:51,190 --> 00:53:57,290
如果我秃了 而且是有色人种
Say I was bald and had the complexion of a popular primary color.

915
00:53:57,320 --> 00:54:00,330
