Just,just a technical glitch.

925
00:54:50,600 --> 00:54:51,870
别看
Don't look yet.

926
00:54:52,200 --> 00:54:54,050
我错了
My bad.

927
00:54:57,240 --> 00:54:58,820
刚说到哪了?
Where were we?

928
00:55:01,400 --> 00:55:03,150
别动
Now,now,hold on.

929
00:55:03,150 --> 00:55:03,740
你!
YOU!

930
00:55:23,940 --> 00:55:26,580
听我解释
I can explain.

931
00:55:28,360 --> 00:55:30,350
你刚才说的那些话呢?
What about everything you just said?

932
00:55:30,350 --> 00:55:32,650
关于以貌取人
About judging a book by it's cover.

933
00:55:32,650 --> 00:55:36,000
先得看看目录好吗?
Well let's take a look at the contents then,shall we?

934
00:55:36,000 --> 00:55:37,430
你毁了都市侠
You destroyed Metro Man.

935
00:55:37,440 --> 00:55:42,790
你占据了城市并让我爱上你
You took over the city and then you actually got me to care about you.

936
00:55:43,950 --> 00:55:46,690
你怎么这么坏?
Why are you so evil?

937
00:55:46,690 --> 00:55:48,110
耍我?
Tricking me?

938
00:55:48,110 --> 00:55:51,180
你想得到什么?
What could you possibly hope to gain?

939
