好吧 Minion 你是对的
Okay Minion,you were right.

944
00:56:46,240 --> 00:56:49,240
我...我也没错啦
I was....less right.

945
00:56:49,540 --> 00:56:51,830
我们还是重操旧业吧
We should stick to what we're good at.

946
00:56:51,840 --> 00:56:53,720
做坏人
Being bad.

947
00:56:55,020 --> 00:56:56,030
Minion．
Minion...

948
00:57:15,470 --> 00:57:16,470
你
You there.

949
00:57:17,560 --> 00:57:18,560
就你
Yeah,you.

