好了 Titan 是时候出来耍耍了
Okay,Titan it's time to go down,in style.

952
00:58:21,640 --> 00:58:24,060
我听说又冒出来个英雄
I hear there's a new hero.

953
00:58:24,060 --> 00:58:26,490
敢跟我过招
who dares to challenge my evil.

954
00:58:26,520 --> 00:58:29,740
叫什么来着 Titan?
Where is the one they call,Titan?

955
00:58:33,610 --> 00:58:35,990
有种你就来啊
Challenge me,if you dare.

956
00:58:58,810 --> 00:59:00,260
噢 不 我们要掉下去了
Oh no,we're gonna crash.

957
00:59:03,720 --> 00:59:06,330
太丢人了
This is embarrassing.

958
00:59:12,830 --> 00:59:15,020
莽夫 幼齿
Ballsy and incipient.

959
00:59:15,020 --> 00:59:18,810
愚蠢 没责任心
Boneheaded,irresponsible.

960
00:59:19,080 --> 00:59:20,090
粗鲁!
RUDE!

961
00:59:20,090 --> 00:59:22,670
不专业 说的就是你
Unprofessional,that's what this is.

962
00:59:22,670 --> 00:59:26,180
都市侠会让我干等吗?
Would Metro Man have kept me waiting?

963
00:59:26,180 --> 00:59:28,260
当然不会 人家很专业的
Of course not,he was a pro.

964
00:59:28,270 --> 00:59:31,100
嘿 超级大坏蛋 我正想见你呢
Hey,Megamind.You're actually the guy I want to see.

965
00:59:31,110 --> 00:59:32,790
而且 这儿又不是没门
Also,there's a door here.

966
00:59:32,790 --> 00:59:37,040
