Do you have any idea how long I waited for you?

967
00:59:37,040 --> 00:59:38,570
不 不 不 我完全能理解你
No,no,no,I totally understand what you're saying.

968
00:59:38,570 --> 00:59:41,270
你等会儿行不 我正打算通关呢
Could you just shut up for one second,I'm trying to beat this level.

969
00:59:41,280 --> 00:59:43,490
你有想过要来吗?
Were you even planning on showing up?

970
00:59:43,490 --> 00:59:45,130
这是什么?
What's this?

971
