972
00:59:49,680 --> 00:59:51,500
都不是我的
It doesn't belong to me.

973
00:59:51,610 --> 00:59:52,990
你偷的!
You stole it!

974
00:59:52,990 --> 00:59:55,470
- 很帅吧 - 不对 不对 你是英雄
-Pretty cool,right. - Oh no,no,no.You're a hero.

975
00:59:55,470 --> 00:59:57,070
衰人才当英雄
Being a hero is for losers.

976
00:59:57,070 --> 00:59:59,860
没日没夜地战斗 战斗 图什么呀?
It's work,work,work twenty four seven,and for what?

977
