That's why I think,WE should team up.

983
01:00:18,320 --> 01:00:19,960
你?等等!什么?
You?Wait!What?

984
01:00:19,970 --> 01:00:22,440
我的力量加上你的智慧
With my power,and your big headedness,

985
01:00:22,440 --> 01:00:24,270
