01:01:23,730 --> 01:01:25,860
来了!我知道
YES!Yes I know.

1006
01:01:25,860 --> 01:01:29,680
将我绳之以法 天哪 太怀念了
Bring me to justice.Oh god,how I missed this.

1007
01:01:32,990 --> 01:01:35,310
