01:01:42,330 --> 01:01:43,340
太棒了!
YES!

1010
01:01:48,570 --> 01:01:50,520
嘘
Ahh...shhhh.

1011
01:01:52,120 --> 01:01:54,290
滚出来 变态!
Come out you little freak!

1012
01:01:54,290 --> 01:01:56,900
看我把你打得屁滚尿流
I want to see what that big brain looks like on the pavement.

1013
