I'm calling time out.

1035
01:03:27,940 --> 01:03:29,550
休战 休战!
Time out,time out!

1036
01:03:40,540 --> 01:03:43,380
小飞虫 启动保险系统
Brain bots.Initiate the fail safe.

1037
01:03:50,430 --> 01:03:52,740
没想到吧 大块头?
Guess what,Buster Brown?

1038
01:03:52,740 --> 01:03:56,370
这是铜做的 这下你不行了吧
It's made from Copper.You're powerless against it.

1039
01:03:56,380 --> 01:03:58,960
可保险了 用来对付...
It's a very safe metal used to defeat...

1040
01:03:58,960 --> 01:04:00,820
都市侠?
Metro Man?

1041
01:04:00,820 --> 01:04:04,860
你别再拿我和都市侠比了
You,should stop comparing me to Metro Man.

1042
01:04:14,020 --> 01:04:16,810
你跑得了一时 超级大坏蛋 可跑不了一世
You can run Megamind,but you can't hide.

1043
01:04:16,810 --> 01:04:18,720
我们得救啦 我们得救啦
We're saved,we're saved!

1044
01:04:18,720 --> 01:04:20,800
您叫什么名字 新的英雄
What's your name,new hero?

1045
01:04:20,800 --> 01:04:23,400
- Tighten - 谢谢您 谢谢
-It's Tighten. - Thank you,thank you.

1046
01:04:23,400 --> 01:04:25,530
Tighten解放了我们
Tighten has freed us.

1047
01:04:25,530 --> 01:04:27,460
我可没说解放
Oh I wouldn't say free.

1048
01:04:27,660 --> 01:04:30,720
应该说 我将带来新的秩序
More like,under new management.

1049
01:04:34,840 --> 01:04:36,940
你想干什么
What do you want?

1050
01:04:36,940 --> 01:04:41,170
- Titan走上邪路啦 - 恭喜 你又一个天才计划弄巧成拙
-Titan's turned evil. - Congratulations,another one of your genius plans has backfired on you.

1051
01:04:41,480 --> 01:04:43,720
门卫怎么会让你上来的
And why did my doorman let you up?

1052
01:04:44,220 --> 01:04:48,240
- Carlos - 你想干嘛 别关 别关
-Carlos? - What are you,no,no!

1053
01:04:48,250 --> 01:04:49,350
我需要你的帮助
I need your help.

1054
01:04:49,350 --> 01:04:51,770
你怎么会需要我的帮助
Why do you need MY help?

1055
01:04:51,770 --> 01:04:55,780
你是我认识的最有智慧的人
Because you're the smartest person I know.

1056
01:04:57,470 --> 01:04:58,930
你不能躲在这儿
Well you can't hide here.

1057
01:04:58,930 --> 01:05:00,980
铜应该有用啊 怎么就失效了呢
Copper should have worked,why didn't the copper work?

1058
01:05:00,980 --> 01:05:03,020
上一次明明效果超赞的
The copper worked perfectly well the last time.

1059
01:05:03,020 --> 01:05:04,810
铜?你在胡说神马
Copper?You're not making any sense.

1060
01:05:04,810 --> 01:05:08,570
听着 如果找不到Titan的弱点 他会把整座城市摧毁的
Look,if we don't find Titan's weakness.He'll destroy the whole city.

1061
01:05:11,000 --> 01:05:12,830
好吧 要我怎么帮忙
Okay,how can I help?

1062
01:05:12,830 --> 01:05:15,730
我们需要找到答案 你最了解都市侠
We need to find answers.You knew Metro Man best.

1063
01:05:15,740 --> 01:05:20,190
他有洞穴或私人要塞那样的藏身之处吗
Did he have a hideout,a cave,a solitary fortress of some kind?

1064
01:05:20,200 --> 01:05:21,970
任何线索都行
Anything that would give us clues.

1065
01:05:22,390 --> 01:05:25,360
我知道一个地方
Well,there is one place I know.

1066
01:05:27,150 --> 01:05:30,460
你给了他超能力 难道就不能收回么
You gave him these powers,can't you just take them away?

1067
01:05:30,460 --> 01:05:35,150
不行 我忘记把隐形车停哪儿了 解构枪落在车里
I can't,I lost my diffuser gun when I misplaced the invisible car.

1068
01:05:35,150 --> 01:05:36,940
那个晚上 你甩了我
The night you dumped me.

1069
01:05:37,160 --> 01:05:39,300
让我独自一人
Alone.

1070
01:05:39,060 --> 01:05:40,980
在雨中忧伤
In the rain.

1071
01:05:41,670 --> 01:05:43,580
- 你回过头吗 - 没
-Did you ever look back? - NO!

1072
01:05:43,580 --> 01:05:47,490
- 疼 我的脑瓜 - 我们想我们到了
-Oh,my giant blue head. - I guess we're here.

1073
01:05:50,460 --> 01:05:53,720
这儿就是他的藏身之处
So,this is where he hid it.

1074
01:05:53,720 --> 01:05:58,220
过了这么多年啊 我的鞋校
After all these years.My old shhool house.

1075
01:06:00,330 --> 01:06:03,660
我觉得 我该为那天晚上的事情道歉
You know,I think there's an apology in order,for the other night.

1076
01:06:03,670 --> 01:06:05,670
听起来不错 请长话短说
Okay that would be nice.But make it quick.

1077
01:06:05,680 --> 01:06:07,840
还有很多事情要解决呢
We have much more pressing matters to deal with.

1078
01:06:11,240 --> 01:06:16,320
哇 难以置信 这些东西他竟然全留着
Wow,can't believe he kept all this stuff.

1079
01:06:16,730 --> 01:06:19,520
我记得他穿那件披风
Aww,I remember when he wore that.

1080
01:06:19,530 --> 01:06:20,890
能专心点儿么
Can we try to stay focused here?

1081
01:06:20,890 --> 01:06:23,020
当然 你说的对 要专心点
Yes of course,you're right,focused.

1082
01:06:24,210 --> 01:06:26,380
嘿 过来看
HEY!Come over and look at this.

1083
01:06:26,390 --> 01:06:28,470
怎么了 发现啥了
What is it?What did you find?

1084
01:06:30,060 --> 01:06:32,760
呃...看
Um.....look!

1085
01:06:32,990 --> 01:06:35,900
杯子里还有冰块
This glass has ice cubes in it.

1086
01:06:35,900 --> 01:06:37,510
对啊 水冷的时候就会结冰
Yes,that's what happens when water gets cold.

1087
01:06:37,510 --> 01:06:39,630
不对 我是想说
No,what I'm saying is,

1088
01:06:39,630 --> 01:06:44,000
你不觉得没融化的冰块透着古怪吗
don't you think it's a little odd that the ice hasn't melted yet?

1089
01:06:44,000 --> 01:06:45,630
人生之一大谜题啊
One of life's great mysteries.

1090
01:06:51,860 --> 01:06:53,040
嘿
Hey.

1091
01:06:53,050 --> 01:06:54,050
啊~!
AAAAAAAAH!

1092
01:07:05,070 --> 01:07:06,920
我们为您带来可靠报道
We now have a confirmed report.

1093
01:07:06,930 --> 01:07:10,930
Tighten 我们曾以为的城市新英雄 现在已成为邪恶化身
Tighten,first thought to be the City's new hero,has turned evil.

1094
01:07:10,930 --> 01:07:13,850
这座城市从未遭受如此残忍的破坏
The city has never seen this level of destruction.

1095
01:07:13,850 --> 01:07:16,310
如果都市侠还活着
If only Metro Man were still alive.

1096
01:07:16,310 --> 01:07:17,990
- 你还活着? - 你还活着
-You're alive? - You're alive.

1097
01:07:19,020 --> 01:07:19,980
我还活着
I'm alive.

1098
01:07:19,980 --> 01:07:22,560
但我们...看到了你的骸骨...
But..we..we saw your skeleton.

1099
01:07:22,560 --> 01:07:24,730
- 你应该死了 - 你是鬼魂吗
-You were dead. - Are you a ghost?

1100
01:07:23,540 --> 01:07:28,620
你最好给个万分合理的解释
There had better be,an amazing explanation for this.

1101
01:07:29,230 --> 01:07:31,200
说啊 幽灵先生
Speak,apparition.

1102
01:07:40,740 --> 01:07:43,510
好吧 好吧
Okay,okay,okay,okay.

1103
01:07:43,510 --> 01:07:44,940
你们应该知道真相
You both deserve the truth.

1104
01:07:45,300 --> 01:07:47,490
事情要从天文台说起
It all started back at the observatory.

1105
01:07:48,500 --> 01:07:51,530
Roxanne被绑架了 我要去阻止你
Roxanne was kidnapped,I was gonna stop you.

1106
01:07:52,350 --> 01:07:54,420
那天我脑抽了
My head wasn't in the game that day.

1107
01:07:55,000 --> 01:07:58,250
我们的争斗就像走过场 所以...
We were kinda going through the motions.So...

1108
01:07:59,500 --> 01:08:00,990
我用了超速能力
Using my super speed.

1109
01:08:00,990 --> 01:08:02,950
决定让头脑清醒一下
I decided to go clear my head.

1110
01:08:04,220 --> 01:08:10,480
随后我意识到 我们一直都在 重复而愚蠢的角色扮演
Then I realized we had done this same silly charade our entire lives.

1111
01:08:11,100 --> 01:08:13,710
我想要从这种思绪中摆脱出来
I tried to get my mind off how I was feeling.

1112
01:08:14,190 --> 01:08:16,270
但就是钻了牛角尖
But I just felt stuck.

1113
01:08:17,100 --> 01:08:20,570
我意识到 虽然我有超能力
I began to realize,despite all my powers,

1114
01:08:21,220 --> 01:08:24,100
但所有市民都拥有一样我没有的东西
each and every citizen of Metro had something I didn't.

1115
01:08:24,750 --> 01:08:25,940
选择
A choice.

1116
01:08:27,110 --> 01:08:31,130
自打我记事以来 我一直是这个城市的傀儡
Ever since I can remember I've always had to be what the City wanted me to be.

1117
01:08:31,990 --> 01:08:34,030
但我的梦想怎么办呢
But what about what I wanted to do?

1118
01:08:35,190 --> 01:08:37,160
我茅塞顿开
Then it suddenly hit me.

1119
01:08:37,840 --> 01:08:39,610
我也有选择权
I do have a choice.

1120
01:08:40,440 --> 01:08:42,990
我想当什么就当什么
I can be whatever I want to be.

1121
01:08:43,410 --> 01:08:45,960
没人说过我必须做一辈子的英雄
No one said this hero thing had to be a life time gig.

1122
01:08:46,730 --> 01:08:48,420
你也不能就这样抽身退出啊
You can't just quit either.

1123
01:08:49,230 --> 01:08:51,400
所以我有了个绝妙的主意
That's when I got the brilliant idea...

1124
01:08:52,690 --> 01:08:54,090
假死
...to fake my death.

1125
01:08:54,570 --> 01:08:57,560
铜抑制了我的力量!
Copper drains my powers!

1126
01:08:57,560 --> 01:09:00,260
你的弱点是铜?
-You're weakness is copper?

1127
01:09:00,260 --> 01:09:01,600
你的死亡射线从天而降
Once your death ray hit.

1128
01:09:02,390 --> 01:09:04,850
我感到前所未有的自由
I never felt so alive.

1129
01:09:05,010 --> 01:09:07,900
我从附近的护理学校里借来骷髅教具
So I borrowed a prop from a nearby nursing school.

1130
01:09:08,300 --> 01:09:11,220
都市侠终于死了
Metro Man was finally dead.

1131
01:09:11,230 --> 01:09:12,990
音乐男就此诞生
And Music Man was born.

1132
01:09:12,990 --> 01:09:14,120
音乐男?
Music man?

1133
01:09:14,130 --> 01:09:15,590
那样我就不用改标志了
That way I can keep my logo.

1134
01:09:15,590 --> 01:09:16,590
- 神马? - 你神马意思?
-WHAT? - 'Cause of what?

1135
01:09:16,590 --> 01:09:20,280
我终于自由了 还发现了我真正的力量
Finally I'm free,to get in touch with my true power.

1136
01:09:20,280 --> 01:09:22,470
谱写音乐巨作
Weaving lyrical magic.

1137
01:09:22,470 --> 01:09:23,610
听听这个
Check this out.

1138
01:09:23,910 --> 01:09:27,580
我有双眼可以看见
I have eyes that can see

1139
01:09:27,580 --> 01:09:31,310
始终给我指引
right through leaaadd.

1140
01:09:31,180 --> 01:09:33,780
- 糟糕透顶 - 非常高兴您还有音乐才能
-That's horrible. - Granted you have talent,

1141
01:09:33,780 --> 01:09:37,490
但现在外面有个疯子在破坏 我们的...你的城市
But there's a mad man out there destroying our...your city.

1142
01:09:38,480 --> 01:09:39,900
你怎么能袖手旁观
How could you do this?

1143
01:09:40,340 --> 01:09:42,880
整座城市的人民都仰赖你
The people of the city relied on you,

1144
01:09:42,880 --> 01:09:46,890
但你抛弃了他们 让我们成为刀俎上的鱼肉...他的!
and you deserted them.You left us in the hands of,him!

1145
01:09:46,890 --> 01:09:47,990
无意冒犯
No offense.

1146
01:09:48,000 --> 01:09:49,150
不 我和你是一边的
No,I'm with you.

1147
01:09:49,440 --> 01:09:51,540
听着 我们需要你的帮助
Look,we need your help.

1148
01:09:51,550 --> 01:09:54,400
我很抱歉 我真的是
I'm sorry,I really am.

1149
01:09:54,400 --> 01:09:56,520
Um 我已经厌倦了
Um,I'm,I'm done.

1150
01:09:56,520 --> 01:10:00,600
知道吗 小家伙 有阴就有阳
You know,little buddy.There's a Ying for every Yang.

1151
01:10:00,600 --> 01:10:03,930
如果世间存有邪恶 正义必会声张
If there's bad,good will rise up against it.

1152
01:10:04,570 --> 01:10:07,430
我花了很久才找到自己
It's taken me a long time to find my calling.

1153
01:10:08,110 --> 01:10:11,060
现在是时候了 找到你自己
Now it's about time,you find yours.

1154
01:10:16,290 --> 01:10:18,030
嘿 谁需要他
Hey,who needs him.

1155
01:10:18,030 --> 01:10:20,020
我们自己可以打败Tighten
We can beat Tighten ourselves.

1156
01:10:20,030 --> 01:10:22,900
我说我们回恶魔巢穴 拿上雷射抢
I say we go back to the evil lair.Grab some ray guns,

1157
01:10:22,900 --> 01:10:25,730
呼朋唤友 武装起来
hold them sideways,and just go all gangsta on 'em.

1158
01:10:26,540 --> 01:10:27,550
我们不行
We can't

1159
01:10:27,550 --> 01:10:29,790
就这样?你放弃了?
So that's it?You're just giving up?

1160
01:10:29,800 --> 01:10:31,530
我是个坏人
I'm the bad guy.

1161
01:10:31,530 --> 01:10:35,150
我不会拯救城市 我不会迎着落日飞去
I don't save the day.I don't fly off into the sunset,

1162
01:10:35,150 --> 01:10:37,340
而且我得不到女孩的芳心
and I don't get the girl.

1163
01:10:38,390 --> 01:10:39,400
我要回家了
I'm going home.

1164
01:11:09,360 --> 01:11:11,500
除非有人伸出援手
Unless someone comes to our aid soon,

1165
01:11:11,500 --> 01:11:13,380
一切将会毁灭
all may be lost.

1166
01:11:14,540 --> 01:11:17,810
数以千计的市民已经逃离了这座城市
Thousands have already fled the city in a mass exodus.

1167
01:11:17,810 --> 01:11:21,950
余下的被迫在家等候进一步的消息
Remaining citizens are warned,to stay indoors until further notice.

1168
01:11:23,460 --> 01:11:28,610
当局发出警告 不惜代价撤离市区
Authorities have issued a warning,to stay out of the downtown area at all costs.

1169
01:11:40,710 --> 01:11:41,720
Hal!
Hal!

1170
01:11:43,420 --> 01:11:44,430
Hal!
Hal!

1171
01:11:45,610 --> 01:11:49,120
我猜猜 看到我有多牛逼之后
Let me guess,after seeing how awesome I am,

1172
01:11:49,120 --> 01:11:50,750
你终于觉悟了
you've finally come to your senses.

1173
01:11:50,750 --> 01:11:52,240
我对你已经没有兴趣了
Well,I'm over you.

1174
01:11:52,240 --> 01:11:54,040
我是来阻止你 Hal
I've come to stop you,Hal.

1175
01:11:54,040 --> 01:11:57,740
你?哦 好吧 你要怎么做 把我给我报死?
You?Oh,well.Okay,what are you going to do,report me to death?

1176
01:11:57,740 --> 01:11:59,750
我会试着劝阻你的
I was going to try reasoning with you.

1177
01:12:00,000 --> 01:12:02,800
你和我 我们一起工作 很长时间了
You and I,we worked together for a long time.

1178
01:12:02,800 --> 01:12:04,220
我了解你
I know you.

1179
01:12:04,220 --> 01:12:05,650
你不了解
You don't know me.

1180
01:12:05,650 --> 01:12:08,080
你从不曾花时间来了解我
You never took the time to know me.

1181
01:12:08,080 --> 01:12:12,760
这是我们第一次在工作之余见面 也是我快要毁灭这座城市的时候
This is the first time we've hung out socially.And it's when I'm about to destroy the city.

1182
01:12:12,760 --> 01:12:14,240
我想要和真正的Hal谈谈.
I want to talk to the real Hal.

1183
01:12:14,240 --> 01:12:18,220
我要的是那个喜爱自己的职业 也喜爱吃调味料的家伙
I want to talk to the guy who loved being a camera man,and eating dip,

1184
01:12:18,220 --> 01:12:21,910
有些书呆子 却没有Tighten这么恐怖
And being a nerd and being not as scary as the Tighten-Hal.

1185
01:12:21,910 --> 01:12:22,820
太晚了!
To late!

1186
01:12:30,160 --> 01:12:31,250
超级大坏蛋
Megamind.

1187
01:12:33,150 --> 01:12:36,280
你和我还有帐要算
You and I have some unfinished business.

1188
01:12:36,280 --> 01:12:40,710
我会等在都市塔 噢 可别临阵脱逃
I'll be waiting at Metro Tower,oh,and just so you don't get cold feet.

1189
01:12:42,520 --> 01:12:43,490
Roxanne!
Roxanne!

1190
01:12:43,490 --> 01:12:47,560
来啊 Roxi 呼唤你的英雄来救你啊
Come on Roxi,call for your hero to come rescue you.

1191
01:12:48,530 --> 01:12:49,800
超级大坏蛋
Megamind.

1192
01:12:51,010 --> 01:12:53,400
我甚至不知道你在不在听 如果你听到了...
I don't even know if you're listening,but if you are...

1193
01:12:53,870 --> 01:12:56,010
你不能放弃
You can't give up.

1194
01:12:57,480 --> 01:13:01,350
我认识的超级大坏蛋决不会临阵退缩
The Megamind I knew would never have run from a fight.

1195
01:13:01,350 --> 01:13:05,080
即使他知道自己毫无胜算
Even when he knew he had absolutely no chance of winning.

1196
01:13:05,200 --> 01:13:07,400
这是你最可贵的品质
It was your best quality.

1197
01:13:07,720 --> 01:13:10,910
你必须站出来 就是现在
You need to be that guy,right now.

1198
01:13:12,500 --> 01:13:14,310
这座城市需要你
The city needs you.

1199
01:13:16,530 --> 01:13:18,120
我需要你
I need you.

1200
01:13:18,120 --> 01:13:19,720
Roxanne．
Roxanne.

1201
01:13:19,720 --> 01:13:23,980
你有一个小时 别让我等太久哦
You have one hour.Don't...keep me waiting.

1202
01:13:25,560 --> 01:13:27,370
典狱长 典狱长!
Warden,Warden!

1203
01:13:27,370 --> 01:13:31,620
